	<div class="slide">
		<h1>Needs and Costs</h1>
		<h2>Need</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Demands frew 50% from 1969-1973 (growth 5%-10% per year)</li>
			<li>Source:  Water 35%, Coal 50%</li>
		</ul>
		<h2>Cost</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>25000 Hectares flooded over 3.5 Years</li>
			<li>$140 Million</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<div class="slide">
		<h1>Churchill River Study (CRS) and Board of Inquiry (BoI)</h1>
		<h2>CRS</h2>
		<p>Assess the Environmental, social, and Economic Impacts of:
		<ul>
			<li>Damming hte river at the Wintego Site</li>
			<li>Turning the region in to a national or provincial park</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<div class="slide">
		<h1>Output</h1>
		<h2>Harm Underestimated</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Land Claims</li>
			<li>Hunting and Fishing rights for Indigenous Individuals</li>
			<li>Hundresds of archeologicla sites flooded</li>
			<li>Vast medium term ecological harm</li>
		</ul>
		<h2><i>Benefits</i></h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Minimal economic growth for locals - if any</li>
			<li>Direct benifits $314 Million</li>
			<li>Indirect:  1:1</li>
			<li>Costlier than alternatives</li>
		</ul>
